383
00:28:22,617 --> 00:28:24,661
they want to show off, right?

384
00:28:29,874 --> 00:28:32,544
It's the opposite.
They want to protect themselves.

385
00:28:33,545 --> 00:28:36,047
They think they're too weak,
so they use clothes for protection.

386
00:28:37,549 --> 00:28:39,551
It's like an armor.

387
00:28:42,554 --> 00:28:47,058
