of protecting her.

388
00:28:47,142 --> 00:28:48,601
I'm talking about Ms. Ko.

389
00:28:57,444 --> 00:28:58,987
My best friend...

390
00:28:59,654 --> 00:29:02,031
When... When are we
going to have our meeting?

