those kinds of women.

396
00:29:20,175 --> 00:29:22,385
-What kind of women does he like?
-He doesn't like women.

397
00:29:23,511 --> 00:29:26,222
-Does he like men?
-He likes me.

398
00:29:26,306 --> 00:29:30,018
"You're my favorite person
in the whole world, Sang-tae."

