00:29:30,101 --> 00:29:31,936
Gang-tae only hangs out with me.

400
00:29:33,062 --> 00:29:35,690
No wonder he doesn't know how to have fun.

401
00:29:39,444 --> 00:29:41,070
I should make sure he has a blast.

402
00:29:41,154 --> 00:29:42,739
No. Mang-tae.

403
00:29:44,073 --> 00:29:45,575
I gave you Mang-tae.

404
00:29:46,201 --> 00:29:48,578
-What?
-You can play with Mang-tae.

405
00:29:48,661 --> 00:29:49,954
