416
00:30:32,038 --> 00:30:32,872
Sang-tae.

417
00:30:33,706 --> 00:30:36,668
Do you know the story called
King Donkey Ears?

418
00:30:36,751 --> 00:30:40,421
Yes, the guy goes into the bamboo forest
and shouts,

419
00:30:40,505 --> 00:30:42,632
"The king has donkey ears!"

420
00:30:42,715 --> 00:30:45,426
Yes, that's right.
If you keep a secret to yourself,

421
00:30:45,510 --> 00:30:47,554
you end up getting frustrated.

